I did run into a confusing, but unrelated (happens on 28f2ca675f89a764e1ec8eb5671b35357b8677f3 too, see #29792), failure with bdb, only on macOS 13.6.6:

```
FileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: 'llvm-objdump'
make: *** [Makefile:1303: dist/Bitcoin-Qt.app/Contents/MacOS/Bitcoin-Qt] Error 1
```
